# direnv hook — auto-loads the Nix devshell when you cd into the repo.
#
# Requires direnv (https://direnv.net) and the `use flake` extension
# from nix-direnv (https://github.com/nix-community/nix-direnv).
#
# Without direnv this file is a no-op; users without it run
# ``nix develop`` manually.
use flake
